      <link href="https://www.ada.gov/tdd2026.html">ADA Title II Video Captioning Requirements 2026</link>
      <link href="https://webaim.org/articles/screenreader_testing/">AT Testing Best Practices</link>
    </see-also>
  </content>
</methodology>
